metadata.name: Place of freedom
metadata.description:
Away from the hustle and bustle of the city in the snowy mountains on the shore of an icy lake there is a lonely house. The only trace of human existence is a place where you are left alone with nature, losing all amenities and becoming one with this place. There you feel truly free  
//
